    public abstract class C4NativePeer
extends AtomicLong
    This approach doesn't actually solve the peer management problem. It is still entirely possible that the peer whose handle is returned by getPeer will be freed while the client is still using it.

    It also exposes the native handle because anybody can call `get`.
